<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA616_07_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema616_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema616_07_ih_0001 paging">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1_orange" lang="y">직육면체의 겉넓이를 여러 가지 방법으로 구하려고 합니다. <span class="empty_box nemo"></span> 안에 알맞은 수를 써넣으세요.</h2>
      </section>
      <!-- 1페이지 -->
      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3>여섯면의 넓이를 더하여 구해보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/616_05_01.png" alt="" />
              <!-- <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/f1to6.png" alt=""> -->
            </div>
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/f1to6.png" alt="" />
            </div>

            <div class="expression_wrap">
              <div class="question_wrap">
                <span> = </span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="15" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span> + </span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="20" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span> + </span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="12" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span> + </span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="20" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span> + </span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="12" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span> + </span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="15" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span> = </span>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="94" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
                <span>(㎠)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(면 ①의 넓이)=5×3=15 (㎠)</p>
                  <p lang="y">(면 ②의 넓이)=5×4=20 (㎠)</p>
                  <p lang="y">(면 ③의 넓이)=3×4=12 (㎠)</p>
                  <p lang="y">(면 ④의 넓이)=5×4=20 (㎠)</p>
                  <p lang="y">(면 ⑤의 넓이)=3×4=12 (㎠)</p>
                  <p lang="y">(면 ⑥의 넓이)=5×3=15 (㎠)</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li lang="y">
                      직육면체의 여섯 면의 넓이를 더하면 직육면체의 겉넓이를 구할 수 있습니다. <br />
                      ➔ 15+20+12+20+12+15=94 (㎠)
                    </li>
                    <li lang="y">
                      직육면체는 평행한 두 면의 넓이가 서로 같으므로 세 면의 넓이를 구한 뒤 각각 2배 하여 더하면 직육면체의 겉넓이를 구할 수 있습니다. <br />
                      ➔ 15×2+20×2+12×2=94 (㎠)
                    </li>
                    <li lang="y">옆면을 하나의 직사각형으로 생각하여 직육면체의 두 밑면의 넓이와 옆면의 넓이를 더하면 직육면체의 겉넓이를 구할 수 있습니다. <br />➔ 15×2+64=94 (㎠)</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve">
                <div>
                  <button type="button" class="btnVideo"><span lang="y">해설 영상</span></button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- 2페이지 -->
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3>평행한 두 면의 넓이가 서로 같다는 것을 이용하여 구해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/616_05_01.png" alt="" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="input_nowrap">
              <div class="img_area2">
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/n1.png" alt="" />
                <span> × 2 + </span>
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/n2.png" alt="" />
                <span> × 2 + </span>
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/n3.png" alt="" />
                <span> × 2 = </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="15" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span> × 2 + </span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="20" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span> × 2 + </span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="12" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span> = </span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="94" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            &nbsp;
            <span>(㎠)</span>
          </div>

          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- 3페이지 -->
        <article class="page page_3">
          <h3>두 밑면과 옆면의 넓이를 더하여 구해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="question_box justify_center dir_col">
            <div class="img_area">
              <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/616_05_01.png" alt="" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="input_nowrap">
              <div class="img_area2">
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/n1.png" alt="" />
                <span> × 2 + </span>
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/n2.png" alt="" />
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/n3.png" alt="" />
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/n4.png" alt="" />
                <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA616_05_IH/n5.png" alt="" />
                <span> = </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="15" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span> ×2 + </span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="64" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            <span> = </span>
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field data-answer-single="94" text-align="center"></math-field>
            </div>
            &nbsp;
            <span>(㎠)</span>
          </div>

          <div class="btn_area">
            <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
            <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
            <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          </div>
        </article>
      </section>
    </div>
